songs.title: Fillip
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
It's happening soon, it's happening soon
Its scent has been blowing in my direction
To me it is new, to me it is new
And it's not gonna change for anybody

[Chorus]
And it's gonna be
Our last memory
And it's led me on
And on to you

[Verse 2]
It's got to be here, it's got to be there
It's got to be now or I'll lose forever
To me it is strange, this feeling is strange
But it's not gonna change for anybody

[Chorus]
And it's gonna be
Our last memory
And it's led me on
And on to you

[Bridge]
Accuse me
Trust me, I never knew
That you were the one
You were the one

[Chorus]
And it's gonna be
Our last memory
And it's led me on
And on to you

[Chorus]
And it's gonna be
Our last memory
And it's led me on
And on to you
You
